CCFF|text_T1N=Transferred to [[1973\u201374 Southern Football League#Division One North|Division One North]]\n|result9=T1N|result22=T1N\n|col_R=#FFCCCC|text_R=Resigned to the [[Hampshire League]]\n|result21=R\n|update=complete\n|source=[http://fchd.info/lghist/south1973.htm fchd.com] [http://www.rsssf.com/tablese/engsouthernleaghist.html rsssf.com]\n|class_rules=1) points; 2) goal ratio.\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Football League elections==\nAlongside the four League clubs facing re-election, a total of 10 non-League clubs applied for election, eight of which were Southern League clubs. All the League clubs were re-elected.<ref>[http://www.nonleaguematters.co.uk/forum/gforum.cgi?do=post_attachment;postatt_id=3506; A history of admission to the Football League]</ref>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=text-align:left\n!Club\n!League\n!Votes\n|- bgcolor=ccffcc\n|[[Colchester United F.C.|Colchester United]]||[[the Football League|Football League]]||align=right|48\n|- bgcolor=ccffcc\n|[[Northampton Town F.C.|Northampton Town]]||[[the Football League|Football League]]||align=right|43\n|- bgcolor=ccffcc\n|[[Crewe Alexandra F.C.|Crewe Alexandra]]||[[the Football League|Football League]]||align=right|36\n|- bgcolor=ccffcc\n|[[Darlington F.C.|Darlington]]||[[the Football League|Football League]]||align=right|26\n|- \n|[[Yeovil Town F.C.|Yeovil Town]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|14\n|-\n|[[Kettering Town F.C.|Kettering Town]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|12\n|-\n|[[Wigan Athletic F.C.|Wigan Athletic]]||[[Northern Premier League]]||align=right|10\n|-\n|[[Chelmsford City F.C.|Chelmsford City]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|4\n|-\n|[[Cambridge City F.C.|Cambridge City]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|1\n|-\n|[[Nuneaton Borough F.C.|Nuneaton Borough]]||[[Southern Football League|Southern League]]||align=right|1\n|-\n|[[Telford United F.C.|Telford United]]||[[Southern Footba