ttle River (Anticosti Island)]]\n\n'''North shore of Anticosti Island''' (from west to east)\n*[[Huile River]]\n*[[Patatte River]]\n*[[Observation River]]\n*[[Vaur\u00e9al River]]\n*[[Des Petits Jardins River]]\n*[[Ours River (Anticosti Island)]]\n*[[Natiscotec River]]\n*[[M\u00e9tallique River]]\n*[[Saumons River (Anticosti Island)]]\n*[[Schmitt River]]\n*[[Prinsta River]]\n*[[Renard River (Anticosti Island)]]\n}}\n\n== Watershed of south shore of St. Lawrence River (between Ontario border and Etchemin River) ==\n\n=== Watershed of Haut-Saint-Laurent ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Canal de Beauharnois]]\n* [[La Guerre River]]\n* [[Saint-Louis River (Beauharnois)|Saint-Louis River]]\n* [[Chateauguay River]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re-des-F\u00e8ves]]\n** [[Anglais River]]\n** [[Outardes River (Chateauguay)|Outardes River]]\n** [[Trout River (Quebec)|Trout River]]\n** [[Rivi\u00e8re de l'Esturgeon (Chateauguay River)]]\n*** [[Noire River (rivi\u00e8re de l'Esturgeon)]]\n* [[Saint-Regis River]]\n** [[Saint-Pierre River (Saint-Constant)|Saint-Pierre River]]\n* [[Tortue River (Delson)|Tortue River]]\n* [[Saint-Jacques River (Laprairie)|Saint-Jacques River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Richelieu River ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*[[Richelieu River]]\n** [[Lacolle River]]<ref>[http://www.rootsweb.com/~qcchatea/placenames/r.htm Lacolle River]</ref>\n** [[South River (Richelieu River tributary)|South River]]\n** [[Amyot River]]\n** [[Acadia River]]\n** [[Hurons River (Richelieu Valley)|Hurons River]]\n** [[Iroquois River (Richelieu River tributary)|Iroquois River]]\n** [[Bernier River (Richelieu River tributary)|Bernier River]]\n** [[Champlain Lake]]\n*** [[Brochets River (Missisquoi Bay)|Brochets River]]\n**** [[North Brochets River (Missisquoi Bay)|North Brochets River]]\n*** [[Missisquoi River]]\n**** [[North Missisquoi River]]\n**** [[Sutton River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Yamaska River ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Yamaska River]]\n** [[Pot au Beurre River]]\n** [[Le Petit Chenail (Yamaska River tributary)|Le Petit Chenail]]\n*** [[Saint-Louis River (Yamaska)|Saint-Louis River]]\n** [[Salvail River]]\n** [[South-West River (Yamaska River tributary)|South-West River]]\n** [[\u00c9cossais River]]\n** [[Yamaska Sud-Est River]]\n** [[Yamaska Nord River]]\n** [[Noire River (Yamaska River tributary)|Noire River]]\n*** [[Renne River]]\n**** [[Duncan River]]\n*** [[Jaune River (Noire River tributary)|Jaune River]]\n*** [[Rouge River (Noire River tributary)|Rouge River]]\n** [[Chibouet River]]\n** [[David River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n'''West bank of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River'''\n[[Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River]]\n* [[Vaches River]]\n* [[Little Black River (Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River tributary)|Little Black River]]\n* [[Saint-Germain River]]\n* [[Ulverton River]]\n** [[Fraser River (Le Val-Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Fraser River]]\n* [[Saumon River (Le Val-Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Saumon River]]\n* [[Magog River]]\n** [[Lake Memphremagog]]\n*** [[Johns River (Vermont)|Johns River]] (Vermont, United States)\n*** [[Cerises River]] (Qu\u00e9bec, Canada)\n*** [[Black River (Lake Memphremagog)|Black River]] (Vermont, United States)\n*** [[Barton River, Vermont|Barton River]] (Vermont, United States)\n**** [[Willoughby River]] (Vermont, United States)\n***** [[Brownington Branch (Willoughby River tributary)|Brownington Branch]] (Vermont, United States)\n*** [[Clyde River (Vermont)|Clyde River]] (Vermont, United States)\n**** [[Pherrins River, Vermont]] (Vermont, United States)\n}}\n'''South bank of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Massawippi River]]\n** [[Coaticook River]]\n** [[Saumons River (Massawippi River tributary)|Saumons River]]\n*** [[Moe River]]\n** [[Lake Massawippi]]\n*** [[Tomifobia River]]\n**** [[Niger River]]\n* [[Eaton River]]\n** [[Clifton River]]\n** [[Eaton River North]]\n*** [[Newport River (Eaton River No