illes River (Quebec-Maine)|Deux Milles River]] (or \"Twomile Brook\" Maine)\n** [[Chimenticook River]], Maine\n*** [[Eastern Lake (Kamouraska)|Eastern Lake]], Quebec and Maine\n**** [[Pointes River]], Quebec\n** [[Pocwock River]], Quebec and Maine\n*** [[West Branch Pocwock Stream]], Quebec and Maine\n*** [[East Branch Pocwock Stream]], Maine\n* [[Little Black River (Saint John River tributary)|Little Black River]] (named \"Little Black River\" in Maine), Quebec and Maine\n** [[West Branch Little Black River (Quebec\u2013Maine)|West Branch Little Black River tributary)]]\n** [[Campbell Branch Little Black River]], Quebec and Maine\n* [[St. Francis River (Maine)|St. Francis River]] ({{lang-fr|rivi\u00e8re Saint-Fran\u00e7ois}}), Quebec and Maine\n** [[Lake Pohenegamook]], Quebec\n*** [[Boucan\u00e9e River]], Quebec\n** [[Blue River (Saint Francis River tributary)|Blue River]], Quebec\n*** [[Little Blue River (Quebec)|Little Blue River]], Quebec\n**** [[Southwest Blue River (Little Blue River tributary)|Southwest Blue River]], Quebec\n**** [[Prairies River (Little Blue River tributary)|Prairies River]], Quebec\n* [[Crocs River]], Quebec and [[New Brunswick]]\n* [[Baker River (New Brunswick)|Baker River]]\n** [[Branche \u00e0 Jerry]], Quebec and New Brunswick\n** [[North Baker River (Qu\u00e9bec-New Brunswick)|North Baker River]]\n* [[Madawaska River (Saint John River tributary)|Madawaska River]], Quebec and New Brunswick (see next section)\n* [[Iroquois River (Saint John River tributary)|Iroquois River]], Quebec and New Brunswick\n}}\n\n===Saint John River \u2013 watershed of Madawaska River \u2013 Quebec and New Brunswick===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Madawaska River (Saint John River tributary)|Madawaska River]], Quebec and [[New Brunswick]]\n** [[Truite River (Madawaska River tributary)|Truite River]], Quebec and New Brunswick\n*** [[Little Truite River (Truite River), Madawaska County]], New Brunswick\n** [[Perches River (Madawaska River)]], Quebec\n*** [