rth Kempt River]]\n*** [[West Kempt River]]\n** [[Matap\u00e9dia River]]\n*** [[Assemetquagan River]]\n**** [[East Assemetquagan River]]\n**** [[West Assemetquagan River]]\n*** [[Causapscal River]]\n**** [[South Causapscal River]]\n*** [[Sableuse River]]\n**** [[Inconnue River (Sableuse River tributary)|Inconnue River]]\n*** [[Sayabec River]]\n*** [[Saint-Pierre River (Matap\u00e9dia River tributary)|Saint-Pierre River]]\n**** [[Melucq River]]\n*** [[Tob\u00e9gote River]]\n*** [[Humqui River]]\n*** [[Matalik River]]\n*** [[Milnikek River]]\n**** [[Grande Rivi\u00e8re Milnikek Nord]]\n**** [[Vaseuse Rivere]]\n*** [[Rivi\u00e8re du Moulin (Matap\u00e9dia River tributary)|Rivi\u00e8re du Moulin]]\n** [[Patap\u00e9dia River]]\n*** [[Meadow River]]\n*** [[East Patap\u00e9dia River]]\n}}\n\n=== Restigouche River watershed (part in New Brunswick) ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n'''Right bank'''\n*[[Upsalquitch River]]\n**[[Popelogan River]]\n**[[Southeast Upsalquitch River]]\n***[[Little Southeast Upsalquitch River]]\n**[[Northwest Upsalquitch River]]\n*[[Little Main Restigouche River]]\n**[[Gounamitz River]]\n***[[North Branch Gounamitz River]]\n***[[West Branch Gounamitz River]]\n\n'''Left bank'''\n*[[Kedgwick River]]\n**[[Belle Kedgwick River]]\n**[[South Branch Kedgwick River]]\n}}\n\n== Watershed of Bay of Fundy (Atlantic Ocean) ==\n\n===Saint John River watershed \u2013 higher part (Quebec, Maine and New Brunswick)===\n\n'''North bank of [[Saint John River (Bay of Fundy)|Saint John River]]'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Southwest Branch Saint John River]], Quebec and [[Maine]]\n* [[Northwest Branch Saint John River]], Maine\n** [[Daaquam River]], Quebec and Maine\n*** [[Roche River (Daaquam River tributary)|Roche River]], Quebec\n**** [[Onze River]], Quebec\n**** [[Douze River]], Quebec\n*** [[Black River (Daaquam River tributary)|Black River]], Quebec\n**** [[Little River (Black River tributary)|Little River]], Quebec\n**** [[Castors River (Black River tributary)|Castors River]], Quebec\n**** [[White River (Black River tributary)|White River]], Quebec\n**** [[Orignaux River (Black River tributary)|Orignaux River]], Quebec\n*** [[Shidgel River]], Quebec\n**[[Otter River (Northwest Branch Saint John River tributary)|Otter River]], Quebec and Maine\n** [[Northwest Black River (Frontier Lake)|Northwest Black River]] (flowing through [[Frontier Lake (Quebec-Maine)|Frontier Lake]]), Quebec\n*** [[Little Black River (North-East Black River tributary)|Little Black River]], Quebec\n*** [[C\u00e8dres River (Talon Lake)|C\u00e8dres River]], Quebec\n*** [[Devost River]], Quebec\n*** [[Gauthier River (Montmagny)|Gauthier River]], Quebec\n**** [[Little Northwest (Gauthier River tributary)|Little Northwest]], Quebec\n*** [[Leverrier River]], Quebec\n** [[Big Black River (Saint John River tributary)|Big Black River]], Maine (named \"Grande rivi\u00e8re Noire\" in Quebec)\n*** [[Depot River]], Maine\n**** [[Brown River (Qu\u00e9bec-Maine)|Brown River]], Quebec and Maine\n*** [[Northeast Grand River]], Quebec\n**** [[Little William River]], Quebec\n**** [[William River]], Quebec\n*** [[Rocheuse River (Grand Black River tributary)|Rocheuse River]], Quebec\n*** [[Buckley River]], Quebec\n*** [[Ratsoul River]], Quebec\n**** [[Tenturette River]], Quebec\n*** [[Grand Calder River]], Quebec\n**** [[Savane River (Grand Calder River tributary)|Savane River]], Quebec\n***[[Truite River (Grand Black River tributary)|Truite River]], Quebec\n***[[Gobeil River]], Quebec and Maine\n*** [[Saint-Roch River]] in Quebec and [[Rivi\u00e8re Saint-Roch|Shields Branch]] in [[Maine]]\n**** [[Gagnon River (Saint Roch River tributary)|Gagnon River]], Quebec\n**** [[North Saint Roch River]], Quebec\n***** [[West Saint Roch River]], Quebec\n**** [[Rochu River]], Quebec (named [[Rivi\u00e8re du Rochu|Petite rivi\u00e8re Saint-Roch]] in Maine)\n*** [[Cinq Milles River (Quebec-Maine)|Cinq Milles River]] (or \"Fivemile Brook\" in Maine)\n*** [[Deux Milles River (